Darmanitan (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0554: Darumaka
Pokémon
#0556: Maractus →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Darmanitan (TCG Pocket).

Darmanitan has been featured on 15 different cards since it debuted in the Black & White expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Darmanitan cards are normally Fire-type, Psychic-type, or Water-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Darmanitan
